Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:23.85,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}一回目　毆れて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.97,0:02:27.23,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}二回目って　どうだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.57,0:02:34.56,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}偶然じゃないよね　三回目が遭うのは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.08,0:02:37.99,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}変わった人だと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:41.51,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}割と皆いうけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:48.77,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}気になったことは 違うんだ　そこじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.32,0:02:55.39,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}君は多分純粋で　純粋を負けず
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.56,0:03:02.67,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}だから小さな日常にさえ　立ち向かって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.69,0:03:09.83,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}夢を持ってきた言葉じゃ　足りない夢にありが
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:13.38,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}きっとこんな風に始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:16.93,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}新しいトキメキ世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:24.04,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}夢を持ってきた言葉を　知らないふりして行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.07,0:03:28.12,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}トキメキと夢のありか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:23.85,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}第一回 被人毆打
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.97,0:02:27.23,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}第二回又會如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.57,0:02:34.56,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}會有第三回絕對不是偶然吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.08,0:02:37.99,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}真是個怪人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:41.51,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}大家好像都這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:48.77,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}應該在意的事不是那個啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.32,0:02:55.39,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}你或許非常單純 並且不向單純低頭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.56,0:03:02.67,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}所以即便是簡單的日常也會抵抗到底
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.69,0:03:09.83,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}充滿著夢想的話語便是夢想不足的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:13.38,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}一定是像這樣開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:16.93,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}那片嶄新的心跳世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:24.04,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}充滿著夢想的話語 就當作沒有聽過繼續前行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.07,0:03:28.12,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}走向那心跳與夢的所在
