Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.40,0:22:39.66,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}連夢想也與我無緣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.00,0:22:45.65,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}看著天空一句話也說不出來
